*She dreamed that she was wearing the Predacon symbol on her arm.  She 
wasn't able to control herself.  Someone else was controlling her.  She was 
firing on the Maximals and killing them off one at a time.  She saw herself 
killing the Maximals one at a time.  She could see her arm raise her gun and 
fire and gun down one Maximal after another.  But she couldn't control it.  
It wasn't her, it was someone or something else controling her.*

Screaming in her sleep, "NOOO!"  Her body moved under the straps.
